name: NZEarthquake
0: ”Alexa, ask geo net the latest earthquake”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: geo net
des:
Felt an earthquake but don't want the bother of launching the app on your phone? Just ask.
This skill queries GeoNet API's felt (thanks to http://www.geonet.org.nz) quake list and return the latest felt earthquake.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
